name: Charli & Edgar Dance Party
description: @AngeloCreates X @AnnaNatter and her 7 year daughter, Emilia, collaborate across the world! Charli and Edgar dance party. Charli an Edgar dancing to some squishy tunes. Edgar was sculpted by Emilia, and Charli was sculpted by Angelo  - both created in Forger app.  Anna textured and animated our friends dancing together with a jelly blob. Angelo designed the sound in #VR an amplified it Adobe Audition.  Rendered in Cinema 4D and Adobe Premier Pro.
